result.name: Pier 88

reviews.text:
Best buffet hot pot for gathering and chitchat, with choice of beer, herbal drinks, Chinese desserts buffet bar. Fresh meat, seafood, king prawn, eel, 草鯇 are our favourite. Order 1/4 (for 2 peoples) or 1/2 for more to try everything, reservation for big group is recommended.

Staff are always nice despite very late at night and take care everything. Favourite late night restaurant, relax and chill atmosphere.
The dim sum is fine and the atmosphere is satisfactory. However, in a not so busy morning, I waited for over an hour for my food.
Bad service nowadays

My table order a set meal for dinner. Food was decent at first then half way through, all the food stopped coming. Waited a hour and more and nothing came even after we asked multiple times. What is stupid is that the moon-paste buns came before the rice and other dishes (which it normally comes last). You start wondering why a fruit platter takes 1hr to serve...In the end, it took more than 3 hrs to get majority of the food we paid for.

Typical dim sum place, and is very popular on weekends and lunch time.  Prices are reasonable, and food is made to order.  We liked the siew mai with roe, as well as the BBQ pork buns.  The gyoza and steam lotus rice was okay, while the preserved egg and pork porridge was smooth, and had lots of pieces.

If you need sauces like chilli etc, you can grab those at the end of the room.

Ordered and enjoyed their mooncakes a few times, including the custard ones and the Hujian white lotus paste with two yolks.

result.name: 稻香超級漁港

reviews.text: 抵食兼大碟， 服務態度很好

Best buffet hot pot for gathering and chitchat, with choice of beer, herbal drinks, Chinese desserts buffet bar. Fresh meat, seafood, king prawn, eel, 草鯇 are our favourite. Order 1/4 (for 2 peoples) or 1/2 for more to try everything, reservation for big group is recommended.

Staff are always nice despite very late at night and take care everything. Favourite late night restaurant, relax and chill atmosphere.
八點半火鍋放題食物質素ok，抵食，性價比高。銅鑼灣比香港仔分店乾淨。兩間分店 點菜後，常常有甩漏，要重複點菜，有時漏單之後重複詢問夥記才得知缺貨，讓人有點沮喪
地點方便，味道不錯的一間中階食肆，大眾化價格合理。
服務一般。有道側門常有客人出入，开佐門好大風，有一道屏幕可擋住外面的風，但服務员冇开屏幕，好影響客人。
